ins在皮克斯工作了15年，参与了皮克斯从2001年至今的每一部动画长片。《Lou》是他独立导演的首部作品。","date":"2017-06-16","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/f0/c9/230093_o6kw6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/f0/c9/230093_o6kw6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/f0/c9/230093_o6kw6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/f0/c9/230093_o6kw6.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/f0/c9/230093_o6kw6.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":3491,"total":66,"score":6.6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":3,"5":4,"6":23,"7":23,"8":12,"9":1,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":28},{"name":"2017","count":21},{"name":"pixar","count":20},{"name":"欧美","count":17},{"name":"美国","count":7},{"name":"皮克斯","count":6},{"name":"剧场版","count":5},{"name":"3D","count":5},{"name":"原创","count":3},{"name":"欢乐","count":2},{"name":"治愈","count":2}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":9,"collect":96,"doing":1,"on_hold":2,"dropped":9}},{"id":378382,"type":2,"name":"Redone","name_cn":"","summary":"A small robot awakens after many years to find the world empty and overrun by Nature. With only fragmentary recordings from its creator, it wanders out into the ruined city in search of answers.","date":"2017-06-16","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/5b/e1/378382_K0GeN.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/5b/e1/378382_K0GeN.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/5b/e1/378382_K0GeN.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/5b/e1/378382_K0GeN.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/5b/e1/378382_K0GeN.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":2,"score":5.5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":2},{"name":"短片","count":2},{"name":"2017","count":1}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":1,"collect":4,"doing":0,"on_hold":0,"dropped":2}},{"id":197562,"type":2,"name":"吃货宇宙","name_cn":"","summary":"这部电影的故事发生在一个和我们平行的宇宙——美食大爆炸所形成的吃货宇宙，不同的星球诸如面粉星球、大米星球、火锅星球上面生活着不同的吃货们，在这里，以传统食物为形象的主角们，将与意图抹去食物原味和下厨乐趣并统治所